@businessId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000111
@serviceId = replace-me

### Create service
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/services
X-Business-Id: {{businessId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceCode": "SVC-100",
  "name": "Massage 60",
  "description": "Relaxing massage",
  "durationMinutes": 60,
  "bufferBeforeMinutes": 5,
  "bufferAfterMinutes": 10,
  "minAdvanceMinutes": 120,
  "maxAdvanceDays": 30,
  "cancellationPolicy": "24 hours notice",
  "priceAmount": "1200.00",
  "priceCurrency": "CZK",
  "isActive": true
}

### List active admin services
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/services?isActive=true
X-Business-Id: {{businessId}}

### Get service by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/services/{{serviceId}}
X-Business-Id: {{businessId}}

### Update service
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/admin/services/{{serviceId}}
X-Business-Id: {{businessId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceCode": "SVC-200",
  "name": "Massage 90",
  "description": "Deep tissue massage",
  "durationMinutes": 90,
  "bufferBeforeMinutes": 10,
  "bufferAfterMinutes": 15,
  "minAdvanceMinutes": 60,
  "maxAdvanceDays": 14,
  "cancellationPolicy": "12 hours notice",
  "priceAmount": "1800.00",
  "priceCurrency": "CZK",
  "isActive": true
}

### Archive service
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/services/{{serviceId}}/archive
X-Business-Id: {{businessId}}

### Public active services
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/services?businessId={{businessId}}
